info.name: News Aggregator Media Kautsar
info.description:
News Aggregator API Documentation

For setting ETL Cron Jobs, go to server or hosting control panel, then go to cron jobs menu and set command time and command below as cron command

- /usr/local/bin/php /home/mediakau/news-api.mediakautsar.com/artisan etl:news >> /dev/null 2>&1
